{"word":"G4919 - συνθρύπτω - synthrýptō - soon-throop'-to - Break","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνθρύπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synthrýptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-throop'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Break</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உடைந்துபோகப் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to break in pieces, to crush"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <b>&#x03B8;&#x03C1;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C0;&#x03C4;&#x03C9;</b> <b>thrupto&#x0304;</b> (to <i>crumble</i>); to <i>crush together</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>dispirit:</i> - break.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}